description: The goal of the project is to improve social fabric and confidence in the society through participatory discussions on national priorities identified as a result of the first-ever survey on social cohesion.

subproject.corporate outcome: National, regional and local levels of governance expand their capacities to manage the equitable delivery of public services
subproject.description:
Confidence-building and dialogue process on all levels are developed and implemented
Project title: Enhancing Dialogue and Trust Building in Armenia (Social Cohesion)
